LIP,Why would you pick up a rock off the ground?
DR. SHIRLEY,‘Cause that ain’t stealin’. It’s just a regular rock.
LIP,But why would you want a regular rock?
DR. SHIRLEY,"I don’t know, just to have. Like for good luck maybe."
DR. SHIRLEY (CONT’D),A lucky rock? Let me see it.
